<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa daihnak, kannih sinah kan i then tikah kan pe tuah. THLACAMNAK:
 Kannih pakhat le pakhat kan i then tikah, Kan umnak ka cio ah Pathian nih
 kan bawm ko seh. Amen.</lyrics>
<title>C.E THLAHNAK HLA CH508</title>
<hymn_number>508</hymn_number>
</song>